videos.headline: Nisby fights to get in end zone
videos.description: Texas Tech capitalizes on an interception as Desmond Nisby scores a 4-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Kempt caps off long Iowa State drive with TD
videos.description: Kyle Kempt caps off a 14-play drive with a 13-yard touchdown pass to Allen Lazard.

videos.headline: Payne recovers fumble for Iowa State
videos.description: Trever Ryen delivers a big hit that forces Justin Stockton to fumble deep in Iowa State territory that leads to a field goal.

videos.headline: Iowa State forces another fumble
videos.description: Desmond Nisby coughs it up as Texas Tech fumbles for the second straight possession.

videos.headline: Kempt tosses 2nd TD
videos.description: Kyle Kempt connects with Matthew Eaton for a 4-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Kempt  uses legs to set up short TD pass
videos.description: Kyle Kempt gets loose outside of the pocket to set up a 3-yard touchdown pass to Matthew Eaton.

videos.headline: Shimonek escapes for TD
videos.description: Nic Shimonek rolls out to the right side and finds the end zone for the 2-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Montgomery can't be brought down
videos.description: David Montgomery takes on a few tacklers and doesn't go down for a 5-yard gain.

videos.headline: Montgomery channeling inner beast mode
videos.description: David Montgomery bounces off tacklers for a 58-yard gain.
